== 2014-11-10 v2.3.0

* Ticket reaction metrics (reaction time, first response time, resolve time)
* Contact selection fixes
* Setting for disable striping HTML tags
* Serbian translation (Radenko)

== 2014-10-02 v2.2.13

* Spent time reports for customer
